ecqm.dataelement

EncounterInpatient

Description:
Clinical Focus: This set of values identify the most common inpatient encounter types.
Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify patients who have had an inpatient encounter. Using the Quality Data Model, this particular element will map to the 'encounter' category.
Inclusion Criteria: Only SNOMED CT codes representing inpatient encounter should be included.
Exclusion Criteria: None.
ActivityCode constrained to codes in the Encounter Inpatient valueset (2.16.840.1.113883.3.666.5.307).
Based On: Encounter
